plot: Batwoman's abilities are tested like never before, while Alice's search for Kate continues; Sophie and Jacob set their sights on Coryana; Luke and Mary contend with an unexpected guest.

Batwoman follows Alice to get a Desert Rose to cure herself of the radiation poisoning that is slowly killing her. Meanwhile, Alice tries to bargain with Safiyah using Ocean's dead body to try and get Kate back.. so she can kill her twin sister.—Gislef
